Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.70,0:00:04.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Linda's late.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.80,0:00:13.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What...? But you and Banri-senpai are so close!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.71,0:00:16.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You always go home together.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.71,0:00:19.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We were convinced you were dating.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.85,0:00:22.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.15,0:00:24.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, are you guys stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.22,0:00:27.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I look out for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.49,0:00:29.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You know, Banri's unreliable.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.99,0:00:31.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I just can't leave him alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.33,0:00:33.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.73,0:00:37.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You're saying you can't leave\NBanri-senpai alone because you like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.23,0:00:38.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.73,0:00:41.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even see him as a guy in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.20,0:00:43.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,There you go again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.27,0:00:45.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You actually like him, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.34,0:00:46.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.71,0:00:48.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like him at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.41,0:00:53.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. Let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.45,0:01:00.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Banri, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.73,0:01:11.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Banri!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.40,0:01:14.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Banri!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.15,0:01:25.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Banri...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.89,0:01:34.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Banri, about the other day...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.96,0:01:40.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like him at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.57,0:01:51.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's so cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.42,0:02:09.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's all the opposite, Banri.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.76,0:02:14.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes I'm really stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.70,0:02:19.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me for being stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.94,0:02:24.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.11,0:02:28.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like you at all, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.78,0:02:30.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.68,0:02:35.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry, Banri...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.99,0:02:38.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.16,0:02:41.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.56,0:02:45.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.83,0:02:50.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,In this moment, I think a fire was lit in my heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.33,0:02:54.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Linda said she didn't like me at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.34,0:03:00.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,If those words were the opposite of how Linda really felt...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.81,0:03:05.77,Dialogue3,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\pos(327,306)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}Reset
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.18,0:03:05.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,...then maybe she...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.01,0:03:09.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hand in hand let's go party night!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.18,0:03:12.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kokoro odoru tomerarenai no
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.55,0:03:18.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Naite waratte kimi to no kioku zutto wasurenai
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.27,0:03:28.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hontou no jibun wa doko ni iru toka
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.74,0:03:32.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Otona ni narutte taihen de
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.94,0:03:35.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Ima wa wasurete mo ii kana
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.84,0:03:38.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yoru ga matte iru kara
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.88,0:03:42.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kokoro wo hazumase aeru toki wo
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.25,0:03:45.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hashagi mawareba
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.19,0:03:49.35,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Tsutaetai omoi ni ima
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.96,0:03:52.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kizuite shimaisou de
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.29,0:03:56.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kako to mirai osorete ite mo
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.70,0:04:00.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Karappo no mama ja ugeokenai
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.47,0:04:06.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Tanoshimeba it's all right hajimeyou
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.31,0:04:13.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yana koto zenbu wasurete kimi to issho ni odori akaseba
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.78,0:04:20.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Motto suteki na jibun ni nareru sonna ki ga suru no
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.06,0:04:26.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Owaranai Golden Time gyutto chikazuku kimi to no kyori wa
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.43,0:04:34.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukazu hanarezu mawari michi demo taisetsu ni shitai
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.97,0:04:37.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.67,0:04:39.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yana-san left early?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.57,0:04:40.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.84,0:04:45.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,So, Tada-kun, will you go check on Mitsuo for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.45,0:04:48.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, there's no way I can go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.68,0:04:49.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.58,0:04:53.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I can't go to another man's place when I have a boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.82,0:04:57.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Going behind closed doors with a member of the opposite sex is cheating.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.83,0:04:59.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Y-you're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.86,0:05:01.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going next door.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.96,0:05:03.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.63,0:05:07.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Tada-kun, are you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.30,0:05:08.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.00,0:05:11.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.21,0:05:12.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go check on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.04,0:05:14.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.44,0:05:17.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't forgotten my feelings for Linda.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.61,0:05:15.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.71,0:05:16.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.61,0:05:17.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}I'll call you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.01,0:05:20.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Not even now, as a ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.68,0:05:19.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.15,0:05:25.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,But that has nothing to do with the current Tada Banri.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.65,0:05:22.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.16,0:05:31.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The current Banri... is dating Kaga Kouko.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.70,0:05:34.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.50,0:05:38.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Is this it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.30,0:05:40.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Yana.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.57,0:05:43.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Let me in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.17,0:05:44.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No, seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.84,0:05:46.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not feeling well today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.64,0:05:48.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't push yourself so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.71,0:05:49.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.41,0:05:53.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd make you dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.41,0:05:55.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Do you like meat and potatoes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.88,0:05:57.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No... I really...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.92,0:06:01.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have anything to do today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.19,0:06:05.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking I could stay over.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.19,0:06:07.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, seriously, seriously, seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.90,0:06:10.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, Yana-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.93,0:06:14.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.17,0:06:15.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Banri?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.34,0:06:19.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,My boyfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.41,0:06:24.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.95,0:06:27.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,He's my boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.18,0:06:32.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No one can come between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.62,0:06:34.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We're lovers from a past life.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.76,0:06:35.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.76,0:06:36.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.96,0:06:39.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I was a shepherd in a past life.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.19,0:06:41.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,And I was a nun at a convent.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.60,0:06:43.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Gross!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.30,0:06:47.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,There's something wrong with you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.87,0:06:53.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Y-you saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.21,0:06:55.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Who was she?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.91,0:06:58.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Reina-senpai from the film club.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.28,0:06:59.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I was so scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.98,0:07:02.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,She was shoving her cleavage in my face.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.95,0:07:04.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.79,0:07:08.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.66,0:07:11.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,This room is a mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.63,0:07:12.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.39,0:07:13.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for coming over.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.26,0:07:16.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kaga-san told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.10,0:07:19.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Something happened with Oka-chan again?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.67,0:07:21.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.84,0:07:25.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Yana!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.67,0:07:27.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You won't get away today!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.98,0:07:30.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Chinami, wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.78,0:07:34.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but could you not talk to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.78,0:07:37.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,A lot of people know about what happened at the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.45,0:07:41.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Do you mean forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.12,0:07:43.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.79,0:07:48.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,If that's what you want, then fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.97,0:07:59.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,H-hi...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.48,0:08:02.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,When did you get here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.81,0:08:05.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who just came up next to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.52,0:08:08.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.02,0:08:13.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's the guy who confessed to Chinami at the party and got shot down on the spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.19,0:08:14.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.29,0:08:17.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yana-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.20,0:08:28.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone around me seems to know that Chinami rejected me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.24,0:08:32.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what I do, I feel so self-conscious...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.84,0:08:34.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.74,0:08:37.37,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.18,0:08:42.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I should act normal around Chinami, like nothing ever happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.25,0:08:47.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,But I freak out every time I see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.19,0:08:51.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I feel embarrassed and sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.26,0:08:52.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.66,0:08:54.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I understand how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.70,0:08:59.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yana-san, look at yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.84,0:09:03.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I've got seaweed in my teeth.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.34,0:09:05.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,From that sushi I bought at the convenience store...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.21,0:09:06.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I meant!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.84,0:09:10.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You're attractive! You should be more confident in yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.51,0:09:14.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, you can't keep acting like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.18,0:09:18.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Just like Linda-senpai helped me, it's my turn to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.92,0:09:21.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What did Linda-senpai do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.12,0:09:23.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, 2D-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.36,0:09:28.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, I want to throw a party to cheer up Yana-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.17,0:09:39.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Tada-kun, you're fifteen minutes late!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.64,0:09:40.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.24,0:09:42.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.61,0:09:43.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.08,0:09:48.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy to see you, Tada-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.72,0:09:55.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy to see you, Yana-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.29,0:09:58.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.06,0:10:00.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,...not happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.26,0:10:02.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That's cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.10,0:10:05.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Look, I appreciate what you're all trying to do, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.80,0:10:08.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get why she's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.47,0:10:15.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,When Banri called me, I had just left class with Kaga-san, and she overheard.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.21,0:10:18.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to be with Tada-kun all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.81,0:10:21.37,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.92,0:10:24.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Going to an amusement park was my suggestion.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.52,0:10:26.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't like it, why don't you go home?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.65,0:10:28.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You're just getting in the way here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.29,0:10:30.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, wait, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.49,0:10:31.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kaga-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.80,0:10:36.29,Dialogue6,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\pos(297,92)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\i1}Oka{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.80,0:10:36.29,Dialogue6,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\pos(268,122)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\i1}Chinami{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.83,0:10:38.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-what should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.80,0:10:40.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's Oka-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.50,0:10:42.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Should I answer? Should I answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.44,0:10:44.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yana-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.94,0:10:48.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.81,0:10:52.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.02,0:10:55.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.68,0:10:58.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We're throwing a party to cheer up Mitsuo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.99,0:11:00.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You should come, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.69,0:11:05.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want you to come, but I'm reluctantly inviting you for Mitsuo's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.16,0:11:09.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.63,0:11:10.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.83,0:11:13.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.07,0:11:14.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I used up some of my kindness on Mitsuo again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.73,0:11:15.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}We're at...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.24,0:11:15.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Replenish...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.34,0:11:18.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You...! What did you just do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.74,0:11:19.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You heard me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.51,0:11:22.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,So, what are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.18,0:11:26.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Leave? Or stay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.65,0:11:30.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Oka-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.85,0:11:31.48,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.22,0:11:34.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be waiting at the ticket gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.42,0:11:35.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.32,0:11:40.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could've come with just you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.73,0:11:43.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Let's come back together sometime, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.03,0:11:46.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The pool will be opening soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.03,0:11:47.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Or would you rather go to the beach?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.87,0:11:50.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my! The beach with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.24,0:11:52.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do? I'm so excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.21,0:11:53.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Banri!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.51,0:11:59.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kaga-san, you came to meet me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.28,0:12:01.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.88,0:12:06.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I was so surprised by that phone call!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.25,0:12:10.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I was shocked when Kaga-san suddenly answered and said Yana was there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.09,0:12:13.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I knew I had to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.43,0:12:15.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I was pretty flustered.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.93,0:12:17.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.07,0:12:19.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I brought this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.97,0:12:20.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Noodles?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.30,0:12:22.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.80,0:12:24.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You really were flustered.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.04,0:12:28.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah! I heard you two are dating now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.91,0:12:30.44,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you knew?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.44,0:12:32.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,2D-kun told me the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.78,0:12:35.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen you holding hands, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.58,0:12:37.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You saw that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.89,0:12:39.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I sure did!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.49,0:12:43.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't actually want you to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.13,0:12:46.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to stay out of my sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.89,0:12:48.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kaga-san, you invited her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.06,0:12:52.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I just pitied Mitsuo because he's hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.80,0:12:55.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,He's my childhood friend, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.47,0:12:57.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You can see him,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.57,0:13:01.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,but don't hurt him any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.48,0:13:04.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't do that, leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.28,0:13:07.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.75,0:13:09.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't have anything to do with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.19,0:13:15.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever happens between me and Yana has nothing to do with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.16,0:13:19.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You're dating Banri, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.43,0:13:24.06,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you pay more attention to what you have?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.93,0:13:27.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Give me back my noodles.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.81,0:13:33.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,A-are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.31,0:13:34.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.85,0:13:39.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.71,0:13:40.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's not broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.78,0:13:44.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if it still works.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.06,0:13:50.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,This is Kaga-san, Kaga Kouko.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.49,0:13:54.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,This is my first time filming her with the Okamera.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.13,0:13:54.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.16,0:14:00.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kaga-san... it's hard for me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.04,0:14:03.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I know it may not seem that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.87,0:14:05.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,After all...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.51,0:14:08.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,After all, Yana said...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.71,0:14:12.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,He told me to never speak to him again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.01,0:14:14.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.18,0:14:19.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the only one who can act cute and cry in front of Tada-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.92,0:14:21.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Suck it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.66,0:14:23.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep doing this until you stop crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.76,0:14:26.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kaga-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.03,0:14:27.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You're suffocating Oka-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.73,0:14:29.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Let me know when you're done crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.56,0:14:31.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to keep doing this until you do!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.33,0:14:33.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to kill Oka-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.94,0:14:39.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Are you done crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.41,0:14:40.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,A-are you alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.51,0:14:46.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Banri... don't I look really funny right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.78,0:14:50.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What? You want me to film you? Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.22,0:14:52.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.72,0:14:54.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.09,0:14:59.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kaga-san, could you try letting go?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.06,0:15:03.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It feels really stable right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.73,0:15:05.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.65,0:15:25.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What am I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.43,0:15:36.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,W-well, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.16,0:15:37.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What should we ride first?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.80,0:15:39.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,A roller coaster!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.08,0:15:50.44,Dialogue5,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\pos(160,97)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\i1}HAUNTED{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.08,0:15:50.44,Dialogue5,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\pos(173,206)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\i1}HOUSE{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.70,0:16:11.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Have they made up?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.93,0:16:17.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Tada-kun, look only at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.62,0:16:29.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.62,0:16:33.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's called Face Yakisoba.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.39,0:16:34.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Face Yakisoba?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.72,0:16:35.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.99,0:16:37.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of name is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.16,0:16:38.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Is it good, Yana-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.79,0:16:38.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Have some.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.66,0:16:40.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.99,0:16:40.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Yeah, it's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.00,0:16:43.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, why don't we make a pact?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.67,0:16:45.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,A pact?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.57,0:16:46.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.47,0:16:51.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,If any of us ever decides to hang out or go drinking, like today, we'll all try to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.54,0:16:55.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That way, we'll always have a few people to hang out with.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.34,0:16:56.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.58,0:16:58.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,If Tada-kun's in, I'm in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.81,0:17:01.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like that Mitsuo's involved, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.32,0:17:02.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I could say the same about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.72,0:17:04.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Count me in, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.75,0:17:05.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Ready, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.49,0:17:07.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.87,0:17:22.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Is anyone awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.41,0:17:36.02,Dialogue4,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\pos(126,63)}Linda-senpai
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.41,0:17:36.02,Dialogue4,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\pos(165,143)}No subject
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.41,0:17:36.02,Dialogue4,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\pos(121,289)}Are you awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.02,0:17:36.85,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\pos(371,277)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}Sending
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.02,0:17:36.85,Dialogue4,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\pos(367,313)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}Message
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.70,0:17:50.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Linda... Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.80,0:17:52.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Banri.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.23,0:17:55.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Can I speak casually with you, just for now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.57,0:17:58.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It just feels more right that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.11,0:18:02.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You guys were noisy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.64,0:18:05.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Were you in Nana-senpai's room this whole time?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.82,0:18:11.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I was just reminiscing about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.72,0:18:15.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,So I really freaked out when I got your text.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.76,0:18:18.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,How did you know I was awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.09,0:18:20.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.56,0:18:22.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I just felt like you were.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.57,0:18:27.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You've always been like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.97,0:18:30.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes we'd go on trips with our club.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.64,0:18:32.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever I couldn't sleep,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.64,0:18:37.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,you'd come into the girls' room and ask, "Hey, Linda, are you awake?"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.01,0:18:39.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What? So I was a pervert?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.35,0:18:44.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You did cause trouble doing that, but you'd nervously tell me,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.99,0:18:49.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,"I can't sleep. I'm going to be exhausted at practice tomorrow."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.99,0:18:50.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.66,0:18:55.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I definitely had some naughty intentions.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.20,0:18:55.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.83,0:19:01.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Then when my panties went missing, could you have...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.87,0:19:02.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.97,0:19:04.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.61,0:19:16.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You know... for some reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.52,0:19:16.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.55,0:19:21.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I think I used to like you then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.62,0:19:24.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Saying I couldn't sleep was just an excuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.13,0:19:29.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I think I had a sort of perverted desire to watch you sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.56,0:19:31.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,So... sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.84,0:19:42.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We should've talked about the past like this from the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.68,0:19:49.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Once you miss the opportunity to say something, the words become increasingly toxic.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.18,0:19:53.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The best thing to do is to just say everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.82,0:20:00.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing between us that we can't say anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.76,0:20:03.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.86,0:20:06.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We're still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.40,0:20:08.44,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We're looking at the same sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.44,0:20:10.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That hasn't changed at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.37,0:20:13.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Banri?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.41,0:20:17.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I haven't asked you yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.95,0:20:18.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.78,0:20:21.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.28,0:20:25.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,...what your answer to my confession was the day after graduation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.62,0:20:30.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That's obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.06,0:20:34.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It was "no."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.20,0:20:41.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I just couldn't think of you romantically.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.10,0:20:46.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I was going to tell you we should stay friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.31,0:20:50.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.08,0:20:53.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Linda... Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.78,0:20:58.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to go back?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.22,0:21:04.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,To that place where I used to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.63,0:21:06.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.23,0:21:09.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.84,0:21:17.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What did I just say?
